---
source: src/core/preflight_guard.rs
assertion: preflight guard evaluates commands against evidence-matched rules
schema:
  guard: ee.preflight.guard.v1
contracts:
  - preflight guard checks command against builtin rules from AGENTS.md
  - preflight guard checks command against workspace rules from .ee/preflight_rules.toml
  - preflight guard returns exit code 0 when no halt rules match
  - preflight guard returns exit code 7 (PolicyDenied) when any halt rule matches
  - preflight guard supports BLAKE3 keyed-hash bypass tokens per (rule_id, command)
  - preflight guard warns but does not halt for action=warn rules
  - preflight guard citations include rule source (builtin, workspace_file, etc)
evidence:
  - PreflightGuardReport.exit_code
  - PreflightGuardReport.matches
  - GuardMatch.rule_id
  - GuardMatch.resolution
  - MatchResolution::Enforced
  - MatchResolution::BypassedWithToken
